<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2006-03/uoc--isq032706.php" class="external text" title="http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2006-03/uoc--isq032706.php" rel="nofollow">"International study questions health benefits of moderate drinking"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2006-03/uoc--isq032706.php" class="external free" title="http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2006-03/uoc--isq032706.php" rel="nofollow">http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2006-03/uoc--isq032706.php</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=International+study+questions+health+benefits+of+moderate+drinking&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fpub_releases%2F2006-03%2Fuoc--isq032706.php&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hormesis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.cellmetabolism.org/content/article/abstract?uid=PIIS1550413107002562" class="external text" title="http://www.cellmetabolism.org/content/article/abstract?uid=PIIS1550413107002562" rel="nofollow">Publication demonstrating that oxidative stress promotes life span</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-Bjelakovic-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Bjelakovic_22-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBjelakovic_G.2C_Nikolova_D.2C_Gluud_L.2C_Simonetti_R.2C_Gluud_C2007">Bjelakovic G, Nikolova D, Gluud L, Simonetti R, Gluud C (2007). "<a href="http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/abstract/297/8/842" class="external text" title="http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/abstract/297/8/842" rel="nofollow">Mortality in Randomized Trials of Antioxidant Supplements for Primary and Secondary Prevention: Systematic Review and Meta-analysis</a>". <i>JAMA</i> <b>297</b> (8): 842–57. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1001%2Fjama.297.8.842" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1001%2Fjama.297.8.842" rel="nofollow">10.1001/jama.297.8.842</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17327526" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17327526">PMID 17327526</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/abstract/297/8/842" class="external free" title="http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/abstract/297/8/842" rel="nofollow">http://jama.ama-assn.org/cgi/content/abstract/297/8/842</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Mortality+in+Randomized+Trials+of+Antioxidant+Supplements+for+Primary+and+Secondary+Prevention%3A+Systematic+Review+and+Meta-analysis&amp;rft.jtitle=JAMA&amp;rft.aulast=Bjelakovic+G%2C+Nikolova+D%2C+Gluud+L%2C+Simonetti+R%2C+Gluud+C&amp;rft.au=Bjelakovic+G%2C+Nikolova+D%2C+Gluud+L%2C+Simonetti+R%2C+Gluud+C&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.volume=297&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.pages=842%E2%80%9357&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1001%2Fjama.297.8.842&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/17327526&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjama.ama-assn.org%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Fabstract%2F297%2F8%2F842&